{"tid":551152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人可唔可以唔好咁急躁？","createTime":"2018-02-05T11:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T16:26:23.000Z","uid":88194,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18ba924739c978f54e56cd11adcee666d61b71d9","tid":551152,"uid":88194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"番工放工搭地鐵真係好攞命<br />\n人山人海 逼到死 <br />\n個個都唔中意都唔想 <br />\n好心上車落車就比d耐性慢慢黎<br />\n唔好成日趕住去投胎咁<br />\n仲有咁多人咁逼有碰撞好正常<br />\n唔係有心又無撞到你跌低就算啦<br />\n本身逼地鐵已經無咩mood 但係大家都係咁逼<br />\n比人少少撞到郁到都抑制自己唔好躁<br />\n因為知道人地都唔想既 唔通特登撞你好過癮咩<br />\n但係啱啱真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD人落車衝住出門 大佬啊 前面後面都有人要出<br />\n中間d人就好似夾心咁比你地夾黎夾去 推黎推去<br />\n講真我好努力去讓位比你地出<br />\n但係你地前又推我 後又推我 我連企都企唔穩<br />\n我已經有d躁 跟住比前面撞到唔小心向後郁到個阿伯<br />\n比佢勁大力推左下 我成個人中向前 仲要睥住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好意思 真喺好撚嬲<br />\n麻煩大家以後唔好咁急躁啦 落車慢少少真喺唔會死架"},{"pid":"263006a29bb534520b23c113dce9219c567b5312","tid":551152,"uid":53554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:29:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cc1a6722c4eb5edecb0140924ab532af822af17","tid":551152,"uid":78464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"去轉日本感受下人哋繁忙時間車廂狀況先返來開post."},{"pid":"3e9ba16ce49eef3cf2398f697e7e5dd05ef00d49","tid":551152,"uid":88194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你咪又係燥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都估到有人咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燥還燥 我無發洩喺其他人身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有d情況應該體諒 有d真喺唔得"},{"pid":"8cf45b5db0d160a33644517b89c55de557e4ef75","tid":551152,"uid":88194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去轉日本感受下人哋繁忙時間車廂狀況先返來開post.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可以咁比較架喎<br />\n唔通人地仲惡劣就代表香港無問題咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只喺嚴重程度既分別"},{"pid":"045a953bc5e9dcef0b1bbe7094bf497f08834fd3","tid":551152,"uid":97267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"讓唔到位就行出架車啦 屌你老母有時好趕時間又有班自私精頂撚住個門口 行出車幾秒駛死咩"},{"pid":"9c770e088daf2f9108bedd1c7689c652a80ddb96","tid":551152,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"你咁嬲  咁你算唔算急燥"},{"pid":"736b7cf5542621f5fd51f69b0fd387b44e853d49","tid":551152,"uid":78443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a581f5871151514666e82680fc232a85118f95aa","tid":551152,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:00:35.000Z","msg":"人類自己放棄自由⋯"},{"pid":"57ace73824b6a2ef321b2aa5d8c3486f4dc75938","tid":551152,"uid":35648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:15:22.000Z","msg":"條路唔好咁多路都未識行嘅撚屌咪無咁燥<br />\n上次見住個阿嬸想上電梯，見住條電梯d人迎面落都想走上去，捉到扶手先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6d0474ff7a475609f8481cee96d6b800caa49b","tid":551152,"uid":88194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讓唔到位就行出架車啦 屌你老母有時好趕時間又有班自私精頂撚住個門口 行出車幾秒駛死咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺 不過有時想行都行唔到 明唔明"},{"pid":"21a77fdd5396fe2a1ca29e9f639fca905bdfd5e2","tid":551152,"uid":88194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條路唔好咁多路都未識行嘅撚屌咪無咁燥<br />\n上次見住個阿嬸想上電梯，見住條電梯d人迎面落都想走上去，捉到扶手先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img